The information provided in this “Additional European Privacy Disclosures” section applies only to individuals located in Europe.
1.  Personal Data
References to “personal data” in this Privacy Notice are equivalent to “personal data” governed by European data protection
			legislation.
2.
Controller and Processor
Tablet is a controller with respect to the personal data we collect to create and maintain consumers’ Tablet accounts or memberships, or
				when we interact with consumers about Tablet’s own services.
Tablet is a processor and service provider to hotels in facilitating your bookings.  When you book a hotel through Tablet, you also direct
				us to share your details with the hotel to facilitate the booking.  You should refer to the hotel’s privacy notice for information about the hotel’s privacy practices
				because this Privacy Notice does not govern the hotel’s handling of your information.
